### 订单分页查询 - 第 1 页，每页 10 条（管理员）
# 说明：该接口沿用订单列表权限校验，管理员 token 需要具备 order:list 权限。
# 预期返回 JSON 示例：
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "操作成功",
#   "data": {
#     "total": 21,
#     "pageNum": 1,
#     "pageSize": 10,
#     "pages": 3,
#     "records": [
#       {
#         "id": 21,
#         "orderNo": "ORD1717214400000",
#         "userId": 1,
#         "amount": 99.90,
#         "status": 0,
#         "remark": "测试订单",
#         "createTime": "2024-06-01T12:00:00",
#         "updateTime": "2024-06-01T12:00:00"
#       }
#     ]
#   }
# }
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer 管理员token

### 订单分页查询 - 第 2 页，每页 5 条（管理员）
# 预期返回 JSON 示例：
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "操作成功",
#   "data": {
#     "total": 21,
#     "pageNum": 2,
#     "pageSize": 5,
#     "pages": 5,
#     "records": [
#       {
#         "id": 16,
#         "orderNo": "ORD1717214300000",
#         "userId": 1,
#         "amount": 59.90,
#         "status": 1,
#         "remark": "测试订单",
#         "createTime": "2024-06-01T11:50:00",
#         "updateTime": "2024-06-01T11:55:00"
#       }
#     ]
#   }
# }
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/page?pageNum=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer 管理员token

### 订单分页查询 - 按 status 筛选（管理员）
# status 示例：0=待支付，1=已支付，2=已发货，3=已完成，4=已取消
# 预期返回 JSON 示例：
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "操作成功",
#   "data": {
#     "total": 8,
#     "pageNum": 1,
#     "pageSize": 10,
#     "pages": 1,
#     "records": [
#       {
#         "id": 16,
#         "orderNo": "ORD1717214300000",
#         "userId": 1,
#         "amount": 59.90,
#         "status": 1,
#         "remark": "已支付订单",
#         "createTime": "2024-06-01T11:50:00",
#         "updateTime": "2024-06-01T11:55:00"
#       }
#     ]
#   }
# }
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&status=1
Authorization: Bearer 管理员token
